summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A GRACO NAUTILUS CHILD RESTRAINT SEAT (NA), MODEL NUMBER: 1763462 AND MANUFACTURED JULY 29, 2011. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE HARNESS BUCKLE WAS HARD TO LOCK AND EVENTUALLY BECAME STUCK WHILE THE CHILD WAS OCCUPYING THE SEAT. THE CONTACT HAD TO THE CALL THE FIRE DEPARTMENT TO ASSIST HOWEVER, THE FIRE DEPARTMENT WAS ALSO UNABLE TO UNLOCK THE BUCKLE AND HAD THE SEVERE THE STRAP AROUND THE CHILD'S LEGS IN ORDER TO RELEASE THE CHILD FROM THE CHILD SEAT. THE MANUFACTURER WAS MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE.
